OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775131865
OL,3,CPolice video shows violent watch thief
OL,4,Chiding under duvet during arrest
OL,6,FA violent watch thief who stole a
OL,7,FRolex worth more than #10,000 at
OL,8,Fknifepoint was caught screaming and
OL,9,Ftrying to hide under his duvet, when
OL,10,Fpolice arrested him at his home.
OL,12,FJason Wokeh, 20, arranged to view the
OL,13,FRolex at the seller's house in
OL,14,FShepway, Kent, on August 19, 2025.
OL,16,FHe asked several questions before
OL,17,Fbeing handed the watch and its
OL,18,Fpaperwork.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
