OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775131865
OL,3,CPolice video shows violent watch thief
OL,4,Chiding under duvet during arrest
OL,6,FWokeh then pulled out a 10-inch knife
OL,7,Ffrom his waistband and threatened the
OL,8,Fman before fleeing the house.
OL,10,FCCTV footage later identified Wokeh as
OL,11,Fthe suspect, with Kent Police officers
OL,12,Farresting him at his home in Woolwich,
OL,13,FLondon.
OL,15,FBodycam footage of the arrest showed
OL,16,Fofficers trying to calm him down as he
OL,17,Fscreamed from his bed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
