OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775131865
OL,3,CPolice video shows violent watch thief
OL,4,Chiding under duvet during arrest
OL,6,FThe stolen watch was soon recovered
OL,7,Fafter Wokeh silently pointed towards
OL,8,Fit, when officers asked him where it
OL,9,Fwas.
OL,11,FWokeh was later charged with robbery
OL,12,Fand threatening a person with an
OL,13,Foffensive weapon.
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty at Maidstone Crown
OL,16,FCourt last October and was jailed on
OL,17,FMarch 23 for seven years and six
OL,18,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
