PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775131865
OL,3,CPolice video shows violent watch thief
OL,4,Chiding under duvet during arrest
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Matthew Lynch said:
OL,7,F"Wokeh attended the victim's home
OL,8,Funder the pretence of being a genuine
OL,9,Fbuyer.
OL,11,FHe added: "(Wokeh) abused the man's
OL,12,Ftrust when he threatened to stab him
OL,13,Fand stole his luxury watch, leaving
OL,14,Fthe victim shaken.
OL,16,F"I am pleased our officers were able
OL,17,Fto deliver swift justice and that
OL,18,FWokeh is now behind bars only months
OL,19,Fafter the offence was committed."
